<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Echo of the Stars</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/particles.js@2.0.0/particles.min.js"></script>

  <style>
    /* Базовые стили */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1473800447596-01729482b8eb?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      color: #f0f0f0;
    }

    #particles-js {
      position: fixed;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    /* Навигация */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 20, 0.5);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #4af;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #0ff;
    }

    /* Шапка */
    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px 60px;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 64px;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px #4af, 0 0 16px #4af, 0 0 24px #4af;
      animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #aaa;
    }

    @keyframes glow {
      from {
        text-shadow: 0 0 5px #4af, 0 0 10px #4af, 0 0 20px #4af;
      }
      to {
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff, 0 0 30px #0ff, 0 0 40px #0ff;
      }
    }

    /* Кнопка */
    .start-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4af, #0ff);
      color: #0a0f1f;
      font-size: 18px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.4s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    .start-btn:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #0ff, #4af);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Секции */
    section {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    /* Нижний колонтитул */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div id="particles-js"></div>

  <!-- Навигация -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#story">Story</a>
    <a href="#characters">Characters</a>
    <a href="#trailer">Trailer</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- Шапка -->
  <header>
    <h1>Echo of the Stars</h1>
    <p>When the stars began to whisper, only a few could hear...</p>
    <a href="#story" class="start-btn">Начать путешествие</a>
  </header>

  <!-- Сюжет -->
  <section id="story">
    <h2>Story</h2>
    <p>In the distant future, humanity has spread across the stars. But a strange phenomenon begins: voices coming from the stars, driving people mad. Only a few can hear them without losing their minds. Among them is Ira Nomiya, a young pilot with a forgotten past. Her journey will uncover the true nature of the voices—and herself.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Персонажи -->
  <section id="characters">
    <h2>Characters</h2>
    <p><strong>Ira Nomiya:</strong> A calm and resilient pilot, able to hear the stars without losing herself. Haunted by missing memories, Ira seeks the truth among the stars.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Трейлер -->
  <section id="trailer">
    <h2>Trailer</h2>
    <p>(Trailer coming soon)</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Echo of the Stars. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

  <!-- Настройка частиц -->
  <script>
    particlesJS('particles-js', {
      "particles": {
        "number": {
          "value": 160,
          "density": {
            "enable": true,
            "value_area": 800
          }
        },
        "color": {
          "value": "#ffffff"
        },
        "opacity": {
          "value": 0.5,
          "random": true
        },
        "size": {
          "value": 2,
          "random": true
        },
        "move": {
          "enable": true,
          "speed": 0.3
        }
      },
      "interactivity": {
        "events": {
          "onhover": {
            "enable": true,
            "mode": "repulse"
          }
        }
      },
      "retina_detect": true
    });
  </script>

</body>
</html>

